可能发生的安全事故，在活动中如发生事前难以预料的及不可抗拒的自然灾害等造成的人身伤亡事故，俱乐部及管理者不承担任何法律、经济和医疗责任。</div><div>8、在活动中如存在质量或服务问题，请及时与领队协调。若领队的解决方式无法让您满意，请直拨领袖户外质量监督电话17706526371，我们会第一时间处理。如果在整个旅行过程中，您没有任何质量方面的反馈，而在结束行程后提起投诉，领袖户外网将无法解决您的问题！</div>";s:6:"online";s:1:"1";s:11:"online_time";s:19:"2017-01-23 11:03:50";s:11:"create_time";s:19:"2017-01-12 15:18:19";s:10:"sell_count";s:1:"0";s:7:"invalid";s:1:"0";s:13:"receipt_price";s:5:"20.00";s:15:"create_admin_id";s:2:"47";s:13:"lock_admin_id";s:1:"0";s:4:"sort";s:4:"1000";s:11:"old_pc_line";s:0:"";s:14:"old_phone_line";s:0:"";s:11:"click_count";s:3:"971";s:8:"articles";N;s:6:"youji1";s:228:"{"title":"这个夏天，我想和你去看海：献给夏天的记忆之——渔山岛之恋","img":"http://img.kllife.com/2017-02-14_58a2ceeb2878a.jpg","desc":"","url":"http://shequ.kllife.com/Index/youjidetail.html?id=1312"}";s:6:"youji2";s:227:"{"title":"【06.24-06.26渔山岛奏鸣曲】奏响盛夏，给你不一样的渔山岛之歌","img":"http://img.kllife.com/2017-02-14_58a2c681181d0.jpg","desc":"","url":"http://shequ.kllife.com/Index/youjidetail.html?id=1386"}";s:6:"youji3";N;s:4:"img1";s:50:"http://img.kllife.com/2017-01-25_5888b3ea65bea.png";s:4:"img2";N;s:4:"img3";N;s:4:"img4";N;s:15:"subheading_show";s:72:"渔山海恋—碧海奇礁，聚焦远海孤岛之美 （2天2夜快...";s:14:"send_word_show";s:153:"渔山岛位于象山最东南，远远望去，宛如镇海之柱立于万顷碧波之中，亦如在蔚蓝色的海天相衬下的一块翡翠，夏...";s:18:"line_especial_icon";s:13:"recommend.png";s:12:"station_data";a:1:{i:0;a:8:{s:2:"id";s:1:"3";s:3:"key";s:8:"hangzhou";s:4:"name";s:6:"杭州";s:8:"attached";s:1:"1";s:3:"tel";s:12:"400-080-5860";s:9:"forbidden";s:1:"0";s:5:"intro";s:27:"领袖户外杭州分公司";s:11:"create_time";s:19:"2017-02-17 10:48:30";}}s:12:"station_show";s:6:"杭州";s:11:"is_xinlvpai";i:0;s:9:"free_line";i:0;s:20:"theme_type_show_text";s:19:"摄影游,周边游";s:15:"theme_type_list";a:2:{i:0;a:3:{s:2:"id";s:2:"38";s:8:"type_key";s:18:"line_theme_sheying";s:9:"type_desc";s:9:"摄影游";}i:1;a:3:{s:2:"id";s:3:"876";s:8:"type_key";s:22:"line_theme_surrounding";s:9:"type_desc";s:9:"周边游";}}s:19:"assembly_point_list";a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:2:"id";s:2:"79";s:8:"type_key";s:9:"undefined";s:9:"type_desc";s:6:"